Package ACO

Class SimulationData

java.lang.Object
ACO.SimulationData
public class SimulationData extends Object
The SimulationData class represents data collected during an ACO simulation.

      public void addCycle(Cycle cycle)
      Adds a cycle to the simulation data. If the cycle is already present, it is not added. Orders the cycles by cost and keeps only the top 6.
      Parameters:
      cycle - the cycle to add

    • getBest

      public Cycle getBest()
      Returns the best cycle in the simulation data. If there are no cycles, returns null.
      Returns:
      the best cycle, or null if no cycles exist

    • getTop5

      public List<Cycle> getTop5()
      Returns a list of the top 5 cycles in the simulation data. If there are 1 or fewer cycles, returns an empty list.
      Returns:
      a list of the top 5 cycles, or an empty list if there are 1 or fewer cycles

    • orderCyclesByCost

      public void orderCyclesByCost()
      Orders the cycles in the simulation data by their cost in ascending order.
